          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Season the <strong>butterflied chicken</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and coat in your <strong>ground turmeric</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> seasoned chicken </strong>to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined tray<strong> </strong>and sprinkle your <strong>nigella seeds </strong>over the top</p><p>Drizzle over a little <strong>olive oil</strong> and put the <strong>nigella chicken</strong> in the oven for an initial 10-12 min or until golden</p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
